$ Windows: Power User Menu
@ Power User Menu

The *Power User Menu* allows to quickly access the following functions in → Windows:
table { ll
  Apps and Features ☰
  Mobility Center ☰
  Power Options ☰
  Event Viewer ☰
  System ☰
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/devmgmt_msc[Device Manager] ☰
  Network Connections ☰
  Disk Management ☰
  → Windows/PowerShell[Windows PowerShell] ☰
  → Windows/PowerShell[Windows PowerShell] Admin ☰
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/Taskmgr_exe[Task Manager] ☰
  → Windows/settings[Settings] ☰
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/explorer_exe[File Explorer] ☰
  Search ☰
  Run ☰
  Shut down or sign out ☰
  → Windows/Appearance/desktop[Desktop] ☰
table }

gh|Windows-Pics|/power-user-menu/opened.png||

The Power User Menu can be opened with the → Windows/keyboard-shortcuts[keyboard shortcut] `windows-x`.

sa:
  → Windows/configuration/Start-menu
